The course specifically deals with the motives behind a number of financial decisions which ranging from individuals to company firms make precisely prior to a big investments. Not only this, we tend to make a number of decisions just on the basis of day in and day out advertisements, however, we in the excitement forget the constant loops of hefty interests and regret, why we didn't think it through before taking loans or making a investment running for a long duration. This course deals with the foundational concepts of Time Value Money, ROI, Loans ( personal/ company).
